Whatever you might think about the new live action TMNT film, this movie tie-in mobile game is surprisingly great fun, with largely excellent presentation and graphics, and a fast, fluid and deceptively simple fighting system that also brings to mind the chain and counterattack brawls of the Batman Arkham games. While there's a few lame enemy designs and player upgrades are more expensive than they should be (no doubt to tempt players into buying IAPs), ultimately the game is something that's well worth checking out, despite its controversial source material. .
